data.description: Welcome to this highly desirable rambler! This charming 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom house is a haven for comfort and convenience. Nestled in a quiet and clean neighborhood, it boasts a spacious, fully fenced yard with convenient RV parking. As you step inside, a warm and inviting living room welcomes you, centered around a lovely fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance perfect for relaxing with loved ones. Whether you're enjoying a crackling fire or hosting gatherings, this space is designed for both comfort and style. This property is not just a house; it's a place where lasting memories are made. Don't miss the chance to make it your own by adding your finishing touch and creating a lifetime of happiness in this beautiful and welcoming home.
